ways to pass arguments to functions
positional arguments - same order the parameters are written
    order matters for positional arguments
keyword arguments - each arguments consists of a variable name and a value (name-value pair)
    frees you from having to worry about correctly ordering your args in function call
    clarify role of each value in function call

Default values - if there's isnt a argument value, python will use the default value of parameter in function

errors about unmatched args
    occur when function is call with too many or too few args
important to use descriptive names for functions and variables